Author: sc0rp1on
Title: [ANN] [Pre-ICO] Whyral - AI Based Influencer Marketing and Evaluation 50% Bonus
Body: Hello, the current smart contract is only deployed to create the token and to disburse the WRL token as soon as a whitelisted address sends ETH. However, in the future we will be deploying smart contracts dynamically which will be associated with the campaigns. These smart contracts will keep track on the work done based on the factor agreed to in the campaign and will send the funds to the influencer based on the target that is achieved. This will permanently remove the association/need of any third party escrow. Also, there are couple differentiating factors among us and other similar projects. 1. The payments to the Brand will be done by smart contract and will be the ROI based making sure the brand is not losing money. 2. We are the only project which aspire to have Alexa for Influencers in which will rank social media Influencers just like Alexa ranks the websites. 3. We are the only project which aspire to create a recommendation platform for the campaigns which will in turn increase the ROI and help both Influencers and Brands.
